                </div>
                <div class="read-more-content">
                                <p>Japan blends ancient traditions with cutting-edge modernity. From the cherry blossoms of Kyoto's temples to Tokyo's neon-lit streets, Japan offers unique experiences including sushi, onsens, bullet trains, and beautiful landscapes like Mount Fuji.</p>
                </div>
