                <div class="read-more-content">
                    <p>Brazil is home to the Amazon rainforest, vibrant cities like Rio de Janeiro with its iconic Christ the Redeemer statue, stunning beaches, and the world-famous Carnival festival. The country offers incredible biodiversity and rich cultural heritage.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Attraction Card 5: Pantheon -->
        <div class="attraction-card">
            <div class="card-image" style="background-image: url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1431274172761-fca41d930114')"></div>
            <span class="price-badge">Free</span>
