                </div>
                <div class="read-more-content">
                    <p>France is renowned for its art, fashion, cuisine, and architecture. From the Eiffel Tower in Paris to the lavender fields of Provence and the French Riviera's beaches, France offers world-class museums, wine regions, and picturesque countryside.</p>
